    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119880/extras/ec664e16121aa9702d94f185304f952d.poster.avif?t=1740968607\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119880/extras/ec664e16121aa9702d94f185304f952d.webm?t=1740968607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119880/extras/ec664e16121aa9702d94f185304f952d.mp4?t=1740968607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Phantom Recall</strong> (Project Yo-Yo) delivers an exhilarating arcade experience, thrusting you into a frenetic arena FPS where every move counts. Master the art of repurposing your lines of fire on the fly amidst a relentless bullet hell to ascend the ranks and dominate the brutal leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engage in dynamic <strong>Shoot</strong>, and <strong>Recall </strong>mechanics with your YoYo.<br></li><li>Charge up your YoYo's damage by striking more enemies.<br></li><li>Splash your flying YoYo to <strong>Push</strong> enemies to your advantage.<br></li><li>Utilize precise recalls to repurpose your lines of fire and turn the tide of battle.<br></li><li>Unleash <strong>Ultimate YoYos</strong> to flood the arena and seize control in bullet time.<br></li><li>Rise through the ranks and establish your dominance on the <strong>Global Leaderboard</strong>.</li></ul>",
